<p>Located about a 25-minute drive from Park City, the Utah has eight bedrooms and 8.5 bathrooms with floor-to-ceiling walnut bookcases.</p>

<p>The house even has its own helicopter pad.  </p>

<p>Described as having 'obsessive focus' by Nikola president Mark Russell, Milton appears to have named his company after Nikola Tesla, the inventor and electrical engineer. </p>

<p>And his company has been regularly compared to and touted as a competitor for Elon Musk's Tesla in the trucks space.  </p>

